name: Structure suitable, with correct stud layout for panel installation
Gib installed and fixed as per gib manual, fixing spacings and location correct
Proclima wrapping applied as per manual, no bubbles. Extora tape to penetrations and extoseal to openings.
Panel primary fixing spacings below maximum design allowance, with correct gauge and embedment depth. Naideck tape installed.
Secondary fixing spacings below maximum design allowance, of correct gauge
Panels correctly coloured, cleaned without defects
